  • Precise Infrared Temperature Measurement: ikago mug warmer is the first infrared temperature measurement mug warmer, which can monitor the temperature of the beverage in the cup in real-time. You can get the temperature you want down to exactly one degree, up to 175. You have complete control over the temperature of your drink and this will be your first step to take control of your life. Note: This product will be affected by other ultraviolet rays, please do not use in direct sunlight.
  • lntelligent Constant Temperature: Since the ikago coffee mug warmer controls the temperature of the drink rather than the heating plate, no matter how much coffee is left in the cup and what the temperature of the beverage is, the ikago smart coffee mug warmer is able to intelligently regulate the temperature and display the drink temperature. Once you find your favorite drink temperature, its able to remember your last setting without having to reset it each time.
  • Smart Security Settings: ikago coffee warmer is equipped with the latest program design, can detect whether the cup is on it through infrared, if the cup is not on it then it will automatically stop heating, if the cup leaves the coffee warmer and enters the standby state more than 15 minutes, it will automatically shut down. If the touch bar is not operated for more than 3 seconds, it will be automatically locked to avoid accidental touch.
  • Advanced Configuration: ikago coffee cup warmers heating plate adopts high quality die-cast aluminum heat conduction plate, has the best heat conduction efficiency, will not break easily. The edge of the heating plate is designed with a waterproof silica gel ring, and the water guide structure is set inside to prevent electric shock by sprinkling water. Panel and touch bar using matte spray process, more quality, and easier to clean.
  • Best Choice For Gifts: Matte black metal style, perfect for office and living room decoration style, ikago coffee cup warmer will be a small household appliance to improve the quality of your life. Excellent design, quality materials, attentive service, we have 3 years warranty, only pay a small price, you can take the first step into the quality of life. Exquisite boxes are also perfect for gifts. Choose ikago cup warmer, and get warm life.

Product description

Meet ikago

ikago Mug Warmer

ikago represents an intelligent life with warmth. Whether relaxing alone or spending leisure time with friends and family, ikago is committed to providing the most suitable temperature with new technology. Its mission is to add the beauty of life with exquisite design so that everyone can enjoy the slow pace of time in between busy work, injecting hope and igniting passions for the new day.

Seize the heat and seize the day!

In the wake of a pandemic that shook the world with its uncertainty and stress, we miss the beauty and importance of slowing down and savoring each moment. A cup of warm coffee may seem small and unremarkable, but in its simple pleasures lie the potential for great calmness and pure joy. Meet the ikago coffee warmer, a pretty nifty little coaster. The ikago coffee warmer makes sure you get perfectly hot coffee with every sip you take. Make a happier and productive day with ikago now!

  • Packing list:
  • 1* ikago Coffee Mug Warmer
  • 1* User Manual
  • 1* Exquisite Box Best For Gift

Digital Display

All temperature readings are accurate within 1 degree and display your coffees real-time temperature. It uses infrared technology to measure the temperature of the coffee in your coffee cup and it can be adjusted up and down in one-degree increments.

High Performance

With patented heating components to increase heating efficiency by 20%, which means that we save more electricity with the same heating efficiency. More than that, with a infarared sensor that ikago can detects cup presence, automatically stops when cup is removed.


Energy-Saving

Infrared detects cup presence, automatically stops heating when cup is removed, resumes heating when cup is replaced. ikago always stays smart.


Auto Shut Down

ikago will automatically shut down with Residual heat reminder if there is no adjustment more than 2 hours or if the cup leaves more than 15 minutes.


Safety Lock

ikago would be locked after 3 seconds when you complete the adjustment. Just move the cup or double-click the adjustment button to unlock ikago.

    This obviously isn't something everyone needs, but it honestly makes my day better! I often get distracted or busy and don't finish my coffee until it's room temp. Not anymore! It's so nice, especially in the winter, to have a warm drink and to not have to... See more
    This obviously isn't something everyone needs, but it honestly makes my day better! I often get distracted or busy and don't finish my coffee until it's room temp. Not anymore! It's so nice, especially in the winter, to have a warm drink and to not have to rush to drink it!

    It's simple to use, one button for on/off, plus and minus buttons to adjust the temp. I've found 140 fahrenheit to be perfect for me.

    I've had no issues with the pressure sensor or temp gauge. It works well at keeping a fresh drink at the desired temperature and also quickly heats up a drink that's cooler.

    It has a slight smell, kind of like a candle wax warmer. I haven't needed the auto shut off but I assume it works.

    Overall, it's definitely worth getting if you want to keep drinks warm.

    Update 2023-01-20:
    ikago has listened to us, and created a new version of this cup warmer. They've dramatically reduced how often it beeps, how loud the beep is, and even reduced how long each beep lasts. It now only beeps when you first turn it on and change the settings, and those beeps are much more reasonable in a typical office environment. It might still be noisy for some really quiet situations or particularly noise-sensitive people, but I thik it fits into a normal home or office environment just fine now. The new version works just as well as previously -- they've dramatically improved the only complaint I and most others have. This is without a doubt the best mug warmer on the market now.

    I modified my original model -- silicone glue in the mouth of the speaker module didn't help, but a squirt of hot glue in the hole did.

    Original:
    The adjustability and accuracy of this mug warmer is really a delight. I'm a recent convert from vacuum-insulated tumblers for my morning coffee. I don't make my coffee until I get to the office, so a desktop solution for hot drinks works just fine for me.

    Unfortunately, as wonderful as the aesthetic design and functionality are, this warmer is totally unacceptable in an office environment. The beep when you turn it on, set the temp, and lift or replace your mug, is WAY too loud. It's louder than most people have their cell phone notifications set in an office setting.

    I think I'm going to have to desolder the speaker. It's not particularly easy to open this thing up -- it's held together by two different sizes of screws, and strong plastic clips. It's hard to move the circuit board -- there are two springs holding it to the case behind the display, and I didn't see an obvious hook to release them. This thing is definitely not built with mods and repairs in mind. But there's something that looks an awful lot like a piezo speaker under the left side of the board (right side when it's assembled). I tried putting a dab of silicone glue in the opening, but that doesn't seem to have helped much. Next step is to desolder it. Otherwise, I'll never be able to keep using this thing at work.

    As an aside, the internal build quality looks pretty good. It isn't grounded, but the live wires are nicely shielded, and the whole body is non-conductive, so it looks quite safe to this amateur.
